    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been assessed. Seven factors achieved their required level; six factors achieved one level below required and were accepted following documented scope negotiation with the regulatory reviewer. Monte Carlo UQ confirms 95th-percentile nIH of 0.0073 g/100L, below the absolute clinical threshold of 0.01 g/100L. The credibility evidence package is deemed sufficient to support the regulatory submission for the Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5.",
